1
00:00:05,060 --> 00:00:07,340
♪The white sail came too late♪

2
00:00:08,100 --> 00:00:10,340
♪Where did he go?♪

3
00:00:11,340 --> 00:00:12,820
♪Snow veils the mountains♪

4
00:00:13,060 --> 00:00:15,340
♪Love endures beyond life and death♪

5
00:00:16,860 --> 00:00:18,580
♪A black chess piece♪

6
00:00:18,660 --> 00:00:22,140
♪Whose game did he stumble into?♪

7
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:26,620
♪All his life, there's no escape♪

8
00:00:28,420 --> 00:00:32,340
♪In ten thousand years, what will still remain?♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:39,020
♪Will anyone still love with an unchanging heart?♪

10
00:00:39,300 --> 00:00:41,620
♪I will remember♪

11
00:00:41,780 --> 00:00:45,660
♪Those days long past♪

12
00:00:46,660 --> 00:00:50,580
♪As the wind drifts with the white sail♪

13
00:00:51,220 --> 00:00:52,660
♪Ten thousand years ago♪

14
00:00:52,780 --> 00:00:56,500
♪Did you once walk this shore?♪

15
00:00:56,740 --> 00:01:01,940
♪Why can't our bond be severed in this life?♪

16
00:01:02,420 --> 00:01:04,100
♪I am lost yet willing♪

17
00:01:04,180 --> 00:01:08,580
♪Still I love you with a steadfast heart♪

18
00:01:11,140 --> 00:01:16,100
♪Until all things fade away♪

19
00:01:22,940 --> 00:01:26,220
♪The stars will remember us♪

20
00:01:26,220 --> 00:01:27,220
[Love & Crown]

21
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:28,980
[Adapted from the novel "My Queen" by Xie Lounan]

22
00:01:28,980 --> 00:01:31,980
[Episode 8]

23
00:01:37,430 --> 00:01:39,410
All the poisons have already been destroyed.

24
00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:42,540
Why then does the Begonia Pendant still react so strangely?

25
00:01:43,950 --> 00:01:46,410
Could it be that there are still other toxins hidden within the palace?

26
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,660
Princess Ying's mind is unclear.

27
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,980
Her words cannot be taken as truth.

28
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,540
Your Majesty,

29
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:04,930
Your Highness,

30
00:02:05,430 --> 00:02:06,770
I mean no disrespect.

31
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:08,290
It is by His Majesty's command.

32
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:11,100
Should a single lamp be lit in this cold palace,

33
00:02:11,590 --> 00:02:13,130
a guard's life must be taken in exchange.

34
00:02:14,190 --> 00:02:15,610
I'm truly fearful.

35
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:42,780
Ying.

36
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:46,410
Ying.

37
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,540
Ying.

38
00:02:58,750 --> 00:02:59,340
Ying.

39
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,660
I'm your brother.

40
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,730
I have come to see you.

41
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:08,260
Qianqing!

42
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,500
Come.

43
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,610
Ying.

44
00:03:23,430 --> 00:03:24,410
It's so cold,

45
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:27,260
remember to keep your shoes on from now on.

46
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:38,820
Ying.

47
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,290
Stop painting.

48
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:42,940
Your brother and I have come to see you.

49
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:47,220
Ying.

50
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:50,260
I brought you osmanthus and red bean dumplings.

51
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,260
After you eat them,

52
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,690
you should go to sleep early.

53
00:03:58,030 --> 00:04:00,290
How did you know I like these?

54
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:09,060
Who are you?

55
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,140
Then do you want to eat them?

56
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:19,250
When I've killed them all,

57
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,730
then I'll eat.

58
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,340
Kill whom?

59
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,220
Why don't you help me,

60
00:04:47,430 --> 00:04:48,410
and kill them all?

61
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,850
Mother, this teacup is exquisite.

62
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:14,540
Fine porcelain,

63
00:05:14,950 --> 00:05:15,730
so clear and delicate.

64
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:19,140
Ying's illness

65
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,730
has always come and gone.

66
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,170
After much effort to nurse her,

67
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:25,460
her confusion still outweighs her clarity.

68
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:27,490
That Xiao Huan

69
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:30,250
is determined to take our lives!

70
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:32,850
Mother.

71
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,900
Ying gave poison to the Empress,

72
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,020
and attempted to assassinate His Majesty.

73
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,580
She was only punished by ten days without lighting a lamp.

74
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,610
That punishment is already merciful enough.

75
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:45,610
Ying has never been of sound mind.

76
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,340
But why did she become this way?

77
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,610
You know the reason well.

78
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:51,460
Had it not been for that great fire at Luling Palace back then,

79
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,100
when Xiao Huan abandoned her,

80
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:55,540
she would never have been so deeply scarred.

81
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,580
Then

82
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:58,780
why did Luling Palace suddenly burn for no reason?

83
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,980
What do you mean by that?

84
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:04,490
You are my own flesh and blood,

85
00:06:04,630 --> 00:06:06,130
the child I carried for ten months,

86
00:06:06,130 --> 00:06:08,140
born through hardship and pain.

87
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,700
Do you not know why,

88
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,100
or for whom, I have done all this?

89
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:20,730
So Mother has always known

90
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:22,170
the truth behind Ying's madness,

91
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,020
yet chose never to tell her,

92
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,900
encouraging her instead to resent His Majesty.

93
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:28,140
Is this, Mother,

94
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:30,460
what you call love for me and Ying?

95
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,660
So,

96
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:45,660
it is because of your sister's matter

97
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,020
that you have borne a grudge against me all this time.

98
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,660
You were in Southern Chu for so many years,

99
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:53,410
yet not once did you send a letter home.

100
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:56,140
Whatever I asked you to do,

101
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,610
you brushed aside carelessly,

102
00:06:57,630 --> 00:06:58,540
and even

103
00:06:59,270 --> 00:07:00,580
stood against me.

104
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,140
Mother.

105
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,050
You speak too harshly.

106
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:18,610
Does it hurt?

107
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,340
It does not.

108
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,020
Mother,

109
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,140
please be at ease.

110
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,250
Now that I have returned,

111
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,410
I shall protect you and my sister with all that I am.

112
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:36,410
I will never let either of you suffer again.

113
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:38,580
The injustice Ying endured,

114
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,540
I will never forget.

115
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:26,580
Well?

116
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,610
Did you meet His Majesty?

117
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,460
Does that mean I can stop practicing?

118
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:31,300
Look at me,

119
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:32,820
do I look like I've met him?

120
00:08:36,030 --> 00:08:37,460
Then what should we do?

121
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:40,300
His Majesty could summon Song Lanxi at any moment.

122
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,610
He values him so highly.

123
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,960
Even if I practice until I'm perfect,

124
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,850
the moment His Majesty sees the real one, I'll be exposed.

125
00:08:46,270 --> 00:08:47,180
His Majesty

126
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,980
is gravely ill now.

127
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,820
He is unlikely to grant an audience for the time being.

128
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,700
As for you,

129
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,010
put your mind to practicing your calligraphy first.

130
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:57,220
We'll talk once you've fooled the officials in the Capital.

131
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,370
Come,

132
00:08:58,510 --> 00:08:59,490
show me.

133
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,770
Your writing

134
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:08,460
does resemble his,

135
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:10,130
yet it still lacks spirit.

136
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:12,370
Anyone who has seen Song Lanxi's true work

137
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,820
will see through it at a glance.

138
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,490
Song Lanxi

139
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:18,580
is a master of calligraphy.

140
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:21,490
A four chi scroll of his sells for more than a hundred liang of silver.

141
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:24,340
How could that be copied so easily?

142
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,420
At the start, you insisted

143
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,370
on accompanying me to the Capital.

144
00:09:30,630 --> 00:09:31,530
You boasted

145
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,420
as if nothing were beyond your ability.

146
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:37,180
I said I wished to go to the Capital with you,

147
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,650
but did I say I meant to impersonate Song Lanxi?

148
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,300
If you think my writing is poor,

149
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,180
do it yourself if you can.

150
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,650
This robe of mine

151
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,300
is

152
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,490
suited to the Dragon Boat Festival season.

153
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,300
It is costly and difficult to make, you...

154
00:09:53,030 --> 00:09:53,820
What now?

155
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:04,010
- What are you doing? - Do not move.

156
00:10:08,780 --> 00:10:10,220
[Turtle]

157
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,890
Do not be angry, Your Highness.

158
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:13,770
Please look.

159
00:10:13,870 --> 00:10:15,460
This is the character I have practiced for over a month,

160
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,580
the one that most resembles his writing.

161
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:17,870
[Turtle]

162
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:18,340
Here.

163
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:23,500
[Turtle]

164
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,580
[Turtle]

165
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,850
Characters like this,

166
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,980
how many can you write?

167
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:37,700
I can write

168
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,180
not many.

169
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,370
About two hundred or so...

170
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:42,370
Two hundred or so?

171
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:44,820
Come,

172
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:46,130
write them all for me.

173
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:48,300
Quickly.

174
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:48,980
Sit.

175
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,130
Come,

176
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:51,250
write.

177
00:10:58,750 --> 00:11:00,460
Your Highness, you're blocking the light.

178
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:11,180
I can't have anyone standing here when I'm writing.

179
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,580
Fine.

180
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:20,300
Hurry and write.

181
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,650
For the Grand Tutor's kindness to me,

182
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:31,980
I would give my body and soul,

183
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,100
and repay it fully.

184
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,490
At the palace examination,

185
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,250
I will

186
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:38,420
take first place.

187
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,060
Good.

188
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,130
You may go.

189
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,340
Well?

190
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:50,300
Any word of Cangcang?

191
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:53,060
She claimed she was going to the Summer Palace,

192
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,420
but went to the Sword Cottage instead.

193
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:00,300
It seems

194
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:03,180
her visit to the Sword Cottage isn't simple.

195
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,770
Then Father means...

196
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,650
Regarding Li Lu's death,

197
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:14,340
she has never let it go.

198
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,820
How is the truth

199
00:12:21,390 --> 00:12:22,690
she seeks coming along?

200
00:13:02,170 --> 00:13:02,990
Master.

201
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,430
I miss you.

202
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:08,580
The longer I stay in the palace,

203
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:12,300
the more I miss the carefree days I had here.

204
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,490
But you're gone.

205
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:18,940
Xiao Huan won't even give me a reason.

206
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:21,700
Master,

207
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:24,420
what exactly were you all hiding from me?

208
00:13:27,270 --> 00:13:28,420
The imperial family is heartless,

209
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:30,010
yet Xiao Huan keeps helping me.

210
00:13:30,390 --> 00:13:32,060
Why is that?

211
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:35,490
Why did you kill my master?

212
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,610
I promised him

213
00:13:39,390 --> 00:13:40,700
I wouldn't tell you.

214
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,610
What did you say?

215
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,250
What aren't you allowed to tell me?

216
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:01,460
What are you all hiding from me?

217
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:21,490
You're back, little glutton.

218
00:14:23,390 --> 00:14:24,340
What do you want to eat?

219
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:25,770
I will make it for you.

220
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:35,580
Master, is it ready?

221
00:14:36,270 --> 00:14:38,340
What gift are you giving me?

222
00:14:40,790 --> 00:14:42,300
You may open your eyes now.

223
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,890
What a beautiful pendant.

224
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:50,250
This is a protector I give you.

225
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:52,250
You must keep it with you from now on.

226
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,220
Well?

227
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,100
Do you like it?

228
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,130
I do.

229
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:57,850
Father never remembers my birthday.

230
00:14:58,150 --> 00:15:00,100
Master is much better than Father.

231
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,180
Thank you, Master.

232
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,490
I really like it.

233
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,890
As long as you like it.

234
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:09,820
Master,

235
00:15:12,150 --> 00:15:13,730
can you tell me

236
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:18,100
why Xiao Huan

237
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,580
had to kill you?

238
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,300
Who?

239
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:30,650
Luo.

240
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,010
Cangcang.

241
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:43,490
Speak.

242
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,250
Why are you here?

243
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,100
I came to pay my respects too,

244
00:15:49,790 --> 00:15:50,770
to share a drink with him.

245
00:15:57,240 --> 00:16:00,580
But Master never drank Bamboo Leaf Green.

246
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:08,370
Are you really here to pay respects?

247
00:16:17,910 --> 00:16:18,700
Cangcang,

248
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:20,370
Father

249
00:16:21,910 --> 00:16:22,980
was worried about you.

250
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,370
Luo,

251
00:16:33,390 --> 00:16:35,420
do you still remember this pendant?

252
00:16:36,150 --> 00:16:37,700
This Begonia Pendant

253
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,770
was given to me by Master.

254
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:45,250
He said it would keep me safe.

255
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:55,730
I remember.

256
00:16:57,790 --> 00:16:59,490
I only learned recently

257
00:17:00,030 --> 00:17:02,300
that it is a treasure beyond price.

258
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:04,050
With it on me,

259
00:17:05,540 --> 00:17:07,990
no poison can get close.

260
00:17:11,110 --> 00:17:13,010
Master was protecting me all along.

261
00:17:18,590 --> 00:17:21,140
But I do not even know why he died.

262
00:17:27,670 --> 00:17:29,930
I do not even know why he died!

263
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,780
Am I that useless?

264
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:42,730
Cang...

265
00:17:54,470 --> 00:17:55,060
Cangcang.

266
00:18:04,430 --> 00:18:05,900
I remember when I was little,

267
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:09,780
I loved leaning against this forge.

268
00:18:10,750 --> 00:18:12,380
No matter how cold it was outside,

269
00:18:13,190 --> 00:18:14,860
it was always warm here.

270
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:52,820
Tell me,

271
00:18:55,230 --> 00:18:57,250
when have you ever approached me

272
00:18:59,080 --> 00:19:00,380
without a purpose?

273
00:19:03,320 --> 00:19:04,340
No, My Lady.

274
00:19:04,990 --> 00:19:05,930
It was Father...

275
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:08,250
Master forged the Rex Sword for you

276
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:12,930
and you used that very sword to kill him.

277
00:19:14,710 --> 00:19:16,780
- How am I supposed to trust you again? - I...

278
00:19:19,990 --> 00:19:22,780
How am I supposed to grow old at your side,

279
00:19:24,120 --> 00:19:25,780
to live with you in harmony?

280
00:19:26,510 --> 00:19:27,930
Since I became empress,

281
00:19:27,950 --> 00:19:29,170
I've swallowed every grievance.

282
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:31,140
In the palace,

283
00:19:32,230 --> 00:19:34,780
there hasn't been a single day I didn't try to uncover the truth!

284
00:19:34,940 --> 00:19:37,020
♪To roam the world with a sword...♪

285
00:19:37,080 --> 00:19:38,170
Tell me the truth!

286
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:44,820
Do you want me to hate you for the rest of my life?

287
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:48,260
