296
00:20:23,710 --> 00:20:25,490
I hate myself.

297
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:28,730
Once,

298
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:33,060
I even thought

299
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:36,820
