307
00:21:00,030 --> 00:21:00,930
Master.

308
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:05,620
♪Looking back across the ends of the earth...♪

309
00:21:06,670 --> 00:21:07,620
Master...

310
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:12,970
I want to...

311
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:16,690
I want to learn sword-forging from you.

312
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:19,250
I'll stay here

313
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:23,410
